@startuml SequenceLogin
title METRIC - Sequência: Autenticação Magic Link (RF010 - SRS)
actor User
participant App
participant ControlPlane
participant AuthAPI
participant EmailService

User -> App: Informa Email
App -> ControlPlane: POST /auth/magic-link {email}
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Criar token mágico
AuthAPI -> AuthAPI: Gerar token (TTL 15min)
AuthAPI -> EmailService: Enviar Magic Link
EmailService -> User: Email com link
ControlPlane -> App: 200 OK

User -> App: Clica no link (app abre)
App -> ControlPlane: GET /auth/verify?token=xyz
ControlPlane -> AuthAPI: Validar token
AuthAPI -> AuthAPI: Token válido
AuthAPI -> ControlPlane: User + JWT
ControlPlane -> App: JWT + User Profile + Orgs
App -> App: Persiste sessão local
App -> User: Acesso liberado
@enduml
